item.title: CVE-2023-27312|2024-09-17T18:11:37.472Z -- netapp -- snapcenter%20plugin%20for%20vmware%20vsphere
item.description: SnapCenter Plugin for VMware vSphere versions 4.6 prior to 4.9 are susceptible to a vulnerability which may allow authenticated unprivileged users to modify email and snapshot name settings within the VMware vSphere user interface.
